---
import BaseLayout from "~/layouts/base-layout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Now · Leonardo Maldonado"
  description="What I'm currently working on and thinking about."
  canonical="https://www.leonardomso.com/now"
>
  <div>
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono text-fg-tertiary text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em]">Now</p>
    <h1 class="font-semibold text-fg text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem)] leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.03em]">What I&apos;m up to</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 max-w-[440px] text-fg-secondary text-[15px] leading-[1.75]">
      A snapshot of what I&apos;m focused on right now. Inspired by
      <a class="link-hover text-fg-muted transition-colors hover:text-fg" href="https://nownownow.com/about" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
        nownownow.com
      </a>.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-16 flex flex-col gap-12">
      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-mono text-fg-tertiary text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Work</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-fg-secondary text-[16px] leading-[1.75] sm:text-[15px] sm:leading-[1.8]">
          <p>
            Recently left
            <a class="link-hover text-fg-muted transition-colors hover:text-fg" href="https://www.namecheap.com" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
              Namecheap
            </a>, where I built
            <a class="link-hover text-fg-muted transition-colors hover:text-fg" href="https://www.spaceship.com" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
              Spaceship&apos;s
            </a>
            domain search platform from scratch as the sole engineer for four and a half years, helping the platform sell 3M+ domains. Exploring what comes next.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-mono text-fg-tertiary text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Side Projects</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-fg-secondary text-[16px] leading-[1.75] sm:text-[15px] sm:leading-[1.8]">
          <p>
            Redesigning this portfolio from scratch with Next.js 16, Tailwind CSS v4, and a custom dark minimal aesthetic. Exploring markdown-powered blogging and modern web patterns.
          </p>
          <p>
            Continuing to maintain
            <a class="link-hover text-fg-muted transition-colors hover:text-fg" href="https://github.com/leonardomso/33-js-concepts" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
              33 JavaScript Concepts
            </a>
            , now at 63k+ stars and translated into 20+ languages.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-mono text-fg-tertiary text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Learning</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-fg-secondary text-[16px] leading-[1.75] sm:text-[15px] sm:leading-[1.8]">
          <p>
            Exploring modern React patterns, server components, and the latest in the JavaScript ecosystem. Always looking for better ways to build for the web.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-4 font-mono text-fg-tertiary text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Life</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 text-fg-secondary text-[16px] leading-[1.75] sm:text-[15px] sm:leading-[1.8]">
          <p>Born and raised in Brazil, now based in Valencia, Spain. Enjoying the Mediterranean pace of life and exploring the city.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-20 text-fg-tertiary text-[13px]">Last updated: February 2026</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
